description:
BIZAIN New Retail Ecosphere Chain (BIZAIN) is committed to build a trusted, open, sharing, union and cooperative multi-level and three-dimensional business ecosystem. It achieved new retail innovative application in the commercial field with block chain technology.

BIZAIN, considering the trend reform between blockchain and new retail, builds innovatively a transparent and trust basic public platform with blockchain characters, to solve the problem of deep integration between offline and online, to reconstruct people, product and market the three industry basic elements, and to realize the resource aggregation and value circulation of all forms of commerce. BIZAIN digital currency token is BIZAIN Token, as BIZ, max supply is a constant 10 billion, and never additional issue.
name: BIZAIN Token
